    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Rust-for-Linux/linux\">https://github.com/Rust-for-Linux/linux</a></p>",
        "id": 358500760,
        "sender_full_name": "LittleKaori",
        "timestamp": 1684165967
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>that's the only change you need, since <a href=\"https://github.com/Rust-for-Linux/linux/commit/593e65924b2e0a74c6292b8e95f1ed16445bdd51\">this commit</a>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">diff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">git</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">samples</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust_hello</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">samples</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust_hello</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a47cf43fba09</span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"n\">ba042cbd712</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">100644</span>\n<span class=\"o\">---</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">samples</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust_hello</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+++</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">samples</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust_hello</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>\n<span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"n\">prelude</span>::<span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"k\">type</span>: <span class=\"nc\">RustHello</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"rust_hello\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">author</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"Rust for Linux Contributors\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">description</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"Rust hello sample\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL v2\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span>: <span class=\"s\">\"rust_hello\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">author</span>: <span class=\"s\">\"Rust for Linux Contributors\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">description</span>: <span class=\"s\">\"Rust hello sample\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span>: <span class=\"s\">\"GPL v2\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">RustHello</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
