    {
        "content": "<p>has anyone got this error :</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">DESCEND</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">objtool</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">CALL</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">checksyscalls</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">INSTALL</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">libsubcmd_headers</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">RUSTC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">samples</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust_hello</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">E0308</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>: <span class=\"nc\">mismatched</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">types</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">-</span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">samples</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust_hello</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>:<span class=\"mi\">26</span>:<span class=\"mi\">22</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">26</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"n\">message</span>: <span class=\"s\">\"on the heap!\"</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">to_owned</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                      </span><span class=\"o\">^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">expected</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"nb\">String</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">found</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"kt\">str</span><span class=\"err\">`</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">error</span>: <span class=\"nc\">aborting</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">due</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">previous</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">error</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
