    {
        "content": "<p>He's following <a href=\"https://wusyong.github.io/posts/rust-kernel-module-01/\">this tutorial</a> for those wondering. <code>to_owned</code> seems to be removed in <code>327cfb66df6947db1618ec0dd339648b0db258e7</code> with the upgrade to Rust 1.70.0</p>",
        "id": 385390677,
        "sender_full_name": "Ariel Miculas",
        "timestamp": 1692172981
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>to_owned</code> assumes allocation to never fail which is not the case in the kernel</p>",
